dct_title_s: خريطة رم السياحية / نظمت وطبعت في المركز الجغرافي الملكي الأردني = Ram tourist map / produced and printed in Royal Jordanian Geographic Centre.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, contours, and spot heights in the map of Ram. Relief shown by shading in Wadi Ram map. Panel title. Includes text, ancillary Jordan road map, 3D view of satellite image of Wadi Ram, and color illustrations.
